<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset CSS */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .otp {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>OTP Verification</h1>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Your OTP for verification is:</p>
        <p class="otp">{{ otp }}</p>
        <p>Please use this OTP to complete your verification process.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>ASTEC Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
